ks.'=>'链接功能帮助您管理友情链接。','The maximum length of the search keyword. Default: 16.'=>'搜索关键词的最大长度。默认 16。','The maximum number of news items returned in the Key-Event message. Default: 5.'=>'以图文格式显示的事件消息最大数量。默认：5。','The message sent to users when they Subscribe the WeChat Official Account.'=>'用户在订阅微信公众号时所接收到的系统消息。','The messages sent to the WeChat Official Account will be stored in the database.'=>'用户在微信公众号里发送的信息，将被存储进数据库。','The nginx server receives the user request'=>'Nginx 服务器接收用户请求','The purpose of OPCache is to improve the efficiency of PHP code through precompiling PHP code. Therefore, our core goal is to reduce the number of file reads and compilation overhead, find a balance between memory usage, cache hit, and code update mechanism.'=>'OPCache的作用是通过预编译PHP代码，从而提高PHP代码的执行效率。所以，我们配置OPCache的核心目标是减少文件读取次数和编译的开销，在内存使用、缓存命中、代码更新机制之间找到平衡。','The system will replace <code>"wp-login.php"</code> with the new address <code>"/oa/$url"</code> below.'=>'系统将使用下方配置的新地址 <code>"/oa/$url"</code> 来替代 <code>"wp-login.php"</code>。','The system will replace the default email templates of the site with custom email templates.'=>'系统将使用自定义邮件模板来替代默认模板。','The system will use SMTP to send emails.'=>'系统将使用 SMTP 来发送邮件。','The theme you configure on the Appearance-Theme page is the main theme of the system. When the option corresponding to the multi-theme mode is empty, the main theme will be used first by default.'=>'您在 外观-主题 页面中配置的主题是系统的主主题。当对应多主题模式的选项为空时，默认优先使用主主题。','The URL you visited is illegal.'=>'您正在访问不合法的网络地址。','Theme Created Successfully'=>'主题创建成功','Theme Customize'=>'主题自定义','Theme Description'=>'主题描述','Theme Editor'=>'主题编辑器','Theme for low-end browsers'=>'低端浏览器主题','Theme for mobile'=>'手机端主题','Theme generated successfully!'=>'主题创建成功！','Theme Install'=>'主题安装','Theme Name'=>'主题名称','Theme URL'=>'主题项目网址','This tab is for Caddy security configuration advice.'=>'当前选项卡是关于Caddy服务器安全配置建议。','This tab is for hybrid theme development advice.'=>'当前标签页是关于混动主题开发建议。','This tab is for Nginx FastCGI Cache